SELECT
    CAST(C_CUSTKEY AS INT)         AS customer_id,
    TRIM(C_NAME)                   AS name,
    TRIM(C_ADDRESS)                AS address,
    CAST(C_NATIONKEY AS INT)       AS nation_id,
    TRIM(C_PHONE)                  AS phone,
    CAST(C_ACCTBAL AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS account_balance,
    TRIM(C_MKTSEGMENT)             AS market_segment,
    TRIM(C_COMMENT)                AS comment
FROM db.customer;

SELECT
    CAST(L_ORDERKEY AS INT)         AS order_id,
    CAST(L_PARTKEY AS INT)          AS part_id,
    CAST(L_SUPPKEY AS INT)          AS supplier_id,
    CAST(L_LINENUMBER AS INT)       AS line_number,
    CAST(L_QUANTITY AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS quantity,
    CAST(L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS extended_price,
    CAST(L_DISCOUNT AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS discount,
    CAST(L_TAX AS DECIMAL(15,2))     AS tax,
    TRIM(L_RETURNFLAG)              AS return_flag,
    TRIM(L_LINESTATUS)              AS line_status,
    CAST(L_SHIPDATE AS DATE)        AS ship_date,
    CAST(L_COMMITDATE AS DATE)      AS commit_date,
    CAST(L_RECEIPTDATE AS DATE)     AS receipt_date,
    TRIM(L_SHIPINSTRUCT)            AS ship_instruct,
    TRIM(L_SHIPMODE)                AS ship_mode,
    TRIM(L_COMMENT)                 AS comment
FROM db.lineitem;

SELECT 
    CAST(N_NATIONKEY AS INT) AS nation_id,
    CAST(N_REGIONKEY AS INT) AS region_id,
    TRIM(N_NAME) AS nation_name,       
    TRIM(N_COMMENT) AS nation_comment
FROM db.nation;

SELECT
    CAST(O_ORDERKEY AS INT)        AS order_id,
    CAST(O_CUSTKEY AS INT)         AS customer_id,
    TRIM(O_ORDERSTATUS)            AS order_status,
    CAST(O_TOTALPRICE AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS total_price,
    CAST(O_ORDERDATE AS DATE)      AS order_date,
    TRIM(O_ORDERPRIORITY)          AS order_priority,
    TRIM(O_CLERK)                  AS clerk,
    CAST(O_SHIPPRIORITY AS INT)    AS ship_priority,
    TRIM(O_COMMENT)                AS comment
FROM db.orders;

SELECT 
    CAST(P_PARTKEY AS INT) AS p_partkey,
    TRIM(P_NAME) AS p_name,
    TRIM(P_MFGR) AS p_mfgr,
    TRIM(P_BRAND) AS p_brand,
    TRIM(P_TYPE) AS p_type,
    CAST(P_SIZE AS INT) AS p_size,
    TRIM(P_CONTAINER) AS p_container,
    CAST(P_RETAILPRICE AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS p_retailprice,
    TRIM(P_COMMENT) AS p_comment
FROM db.part;

SELECT
    CAST(PS_PARTKEY AS INT) AS ps_partkey,
    CAST(PS_SUPPKEY AS INT) AS ps_suppkey,
    CAST(PS_AVAILQTY AS INT) AS ps_availqty,
    CAST(PS_SUPPLYCOST AS INT) AS ps_supplycost,
    TRIM(PS_COMMENT) AS ps_comment
FROM db.partsupp;

SELECT 
    CAST(R_REGIONKEY AS INT) AS r_regionkey,
    TRIM(R_NAME) AS r_name,
    TRIM(R_COMMENT) AS r_comment
FROM db.region;

SELECT
    CAST(S_SUPPKEY AS INT) AS s_suppkey,
    TRIM(S_NAME) AS s_name,
    TRIM(S_ADDRESS) AS s_address,
    CAST(S_NATIONKEY AS INT) AS s_nationkey,
    TRIM(S_PHONE) AS s_phone,
    CAST(S_ACCTBAL AS DECIMAL(15,2)) AS s_acctbal,
    TRIM(S_COMMENT) AS s_comment
FROM db.supplier;
